
# How to install `webpack` and `webpack-dev-server`

```
 npm install --save-dev  webpack@2.2.0
 npm install --save-dev  webpack-dev-server@2.5.0
```

# How to install Babel

```
npm install --save-dev babel-loader babel-core babel-preset-react babel-preset-es2015 babel-preset-stage-1 babel-plugin-transform-runtime

npm install --save babel-runtime
```

# How to run the server

```
  npm run dev
```

```
 npm run build
```
